Subject: RE: [VB] Non-Stock Muffler and Engine Temp

   The next engine going on the dyno will be a 1679, 69X88 cut-ins. This
engine will have stock (new) single port heads, CW crank, balanced etc and a
30 pict 1 carb. One of the things we are going to do on this test is try a
stock exhaust, a 1 3/8 header and a 1 1/2 inch header. We will moniter the
engine heat with different exhaust as well as the change in HP and torque.
   The goal is to see exactly what difference the exhaust will make with
temps and hp on this engine.


ronnie   trying to find the facts


